trans-unit.source: Initializes correlation without sending or receiving a message.
trans-unit.target: Initierar korrelationen utan att skicka eller ta emot ett meddelande.

trans-unit.source: Typically correlation is initialized by sending or receiving a message.
trans-unit.target: Korrelationen initieras vanligtvis genom att skicka eller ta emot ett meddelande.

trans-unit.source: If correlation must be initialized before a message is sent or received, InitializeCorrelation can be used to initialize the correlation.
trans-unit.target: Om korrelation måste initieras innan ett meddelande skickas eller tas emot, användas InitializeCorrelation för att initiera korrelationen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.InitializeCorrelation"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.InitializeCorrelation"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationHandle"></xref> that references the correlation.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationHandle"> </xref> som refererar till korrelationen.

trans-unit.source: This property is read-only at runtime.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen är skrivskyddad vid körning.

trans-unit.source: If the value is set at runtime, an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Om värdet anges vid körning, en <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>genereras.</xref:System.InvalidOperationException>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a dictionary of correlation data that relates messages to this workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger en ordlista med korrelationsdata som berör den här arbetsflödesinstansen meddelanden.
